#: ../../source/basic/updates.rst:8 0e2ea1ca88514cfeba8813ddbe212ba2
msgid ""
"Updates are an important topic in a messaging platform like Telegram. "
"After all, you want to be notified when a new message arrives, when a "
"member joins, when someone starts typing, etc. For that, you can use "
"**events**."
msgstr ""
"在像 Telegram 这样的消息平台中，Updates 是一个重要的话题。"
"毕竟，你总会想要能够在收到消息、新成员加入等情况下收到通知。"
"为此，你可以使用 **events**。"

