#: ../../source/basic/updates.rst:133 31981fa3bee94967955edf73e008f58d
msgid "Entities"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/basic/updates.rst:148 bcddc665c08b4f1abb389532f3151f69
msgid ""
"Events are like messages, but don't have all the information a message "
"has! When you manually get a message, it will have all the information it"
" needs. When you receive an update about a message, it **won't** have all"
" the information, so you have to **use the methods**, not the properties."
msgstr ""

